    <div class="markdown level0 summary"><p>Gets or sets the listener&apos;s forward vector.</p>
</div>
    <div class="markdown level0 conceptual"></div>
    
      
        <div class="codewrapper">
          <pre><code class="lang-csharp hljs">public Vector3 Forward { get; set; }</code></pre>
        </div>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    
    <h id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_Audio_AudioListener_Forward_remarks">Remarks</h>
    <div class="markdown level0 remarks"><p>Defaults to Vector3.Forward. (new Vector3(0, 0, -1))</p>
<p>Used with AudioListener.Velocity and AudioEmitter.Velocity to calculate Doppler values.</p>
<p>The Forward and Up vectors must be orthonormal.</p>
</div>
    
    
    
    

